{"tid":2402624,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我男朋友訓教嗰陣會大聲講粗口鬧人同打人 但係訓醒會佢會唔記得咗件事 應該點面對佢","createTime":"2021-02-10T14:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T14:38:56.000Z","uid":159653,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c0200f850e06ff5cde33072a7de130be3765d355","tid":2402624,"uid":159653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"因為佢細個成日比屋企人打同鬧 even喺佢訓教嗰陣都會無啦啦比人噪醒比人屌 一訓醒就要同人鬧交 搞到佢警覺性好強 訓緊教一有少少衣郁佢就會出手 佢話佢由細到大都係咁 加上佢平時份工好大壓力要對好多客 最大問題佢訓醒完全唔知發生咩事 好似夢遊咁 望住我好嬲咁佢都好似好無奈 好似我嬲錯人咁 但我唔係好接受唔到夜晚無啦啦比人打一錘同無啦啦屌我老母 但佢平時對我好好 係結婚對象 我可以點做？"},{"pid":"0b17b0c4377b68f78416e8907421dcb5eccffdf0","tid":2402624,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"感建分<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1637bb425c6bfe69a0db2c97ba42ed7f4c446586","tid":2402624,"uid":166301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:04:40.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"d6c16847548bd39452895e535aeed989e194e5da","tid":2402624,"uid":116343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"帶佢睇醫生"},{"pid":"3d7fae49832df0eab10c0bc4c9248d29704c994c","tid":2402624,"uid":280223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"建議搵醫生跟跟佢，心理障礙唔係咁易解決"},{"pid":"e8897781a8a3707f681b87f31723310d0baa36d4","tid":2402624,"uid":250905,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqK455d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuqK455d.jpg&h=3b8f8531&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49f55816ba6c05e8438fe23fb387b65fd3e52a28","tid":2402624,"uid":159653,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0b17b0c4377b68f78416e8907421dcb5eccffdf0","tid":2402624,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"感建分<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pr